  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study is to test a decision aid that is designed to help patients make decision regarding
      management of their gastroesophageal reflux disease (GERD). Once the decision aid is
      constructed we will test and assess the aid on ~100 patients who have GERD to assess
      effectiveness.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
